=========================================================
FINAL PATTERN TEST (AFTER DAY 5)
=========================================================

Without looking at solutions, identify pattern only:

1. Trapping Rain Water
2. Fruit Into Baskets
3. Koko Eating Bananas
4. Merge K Sorted Lists
5. Next Greater Element
6. Diameter Of Binary Tree
7. Rotten Oranges
8. Unique Paths
9. House Robber
10. Pacific Atlantic Water Flow

If you can correctly identify the pattern for
8-10 out of these problems within 30 seconds,
your DSA pattern recognition is at a good level
for most senior C++ interviews.
